And to do that, we need to talk about blowing bubbles.

03:02.080 --> 03:02.400
Bubbles.

03:02.400 --> 03:02.760
Yeah.

03:02.880 --> 03:12.900
I mean, to appreciate why this bubble metaphor, what they call the spherepop calculus, is so revolutionary, we actually need to take a quick detour back to the 1930s.

03:12.980 --> 03:13.200
Okay.

03:13.300 --> 03:13.820
Time travel.

03:14.060 --> 03:14.360
I'm in.

