The implications of that are massive. It means we don't need different architectures, different hardware, or different paradigms for symbolic AI, neural networks, or probability calculators.

27:24.440 --> 27:30.140
They're all exactly the same thing. Geometric graph composition. We've just been swapping out the math plugged into the nodes.

